        If False, for some time, the weights will be in memory twice (Full + Reduced),\n        before the garbage collection removes the Full weights from cache.\n        If True, the cache will be emptied, before the reduced weights will be loaded to the device of the model and\n        therefore won't have a temporarily higher memory footprint.\n    optimizer: Defaults to None\n        If provided, the optimizer parameters will be updated, to use the reduced embeddings instead of the old pointer.\n        It is crucial to provide the optimizer if one was created before reducing the model."]}], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "transformer_smaller_training_vocab.transformer_set_vocab.set_vocab_bert", "documentation": [], "functions": [{"name": "transformer_smaller_training_vocab.transformer_set_vocab.set_vocab_bert.set_bert_vocab", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "tokenizer", "type": {"name": "BertTokenizer", "xref": {"fqname": "transformers.BertTokenizer", "project": null}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "vocab", "type": {"name": "Dict", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Dict", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, {"name": "int", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.int", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}]}, "default": null}], "returns": {"name": "None", "xref": {"fqname": "constants.None", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "documentation": []}], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "transformer_smaller_training_vocab.transformer_set_vocab.set_vocab_roberta", "documentation": [], "functions": [{"name": "transformer_smaller_training_vocab.transformer_set_vocab.set_vocab_roberta.set_roberta_vocab", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "tokenizer", "type": {"name": "RobertaTokenizer", "xref": {"fqname": "transformers.RobertaTokenizer", "project": null}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "vocab", "ty